lead_paragraph: Formula One's post-season shake-up took another spin on Tuesday with Williams announcing the departure of technical head Pat Symonds while Valtteri Bottas moved closer to Mercedes and Felipe Massa's retirement looked to be coming to an end.

headline.print_headline: Motor Racing: Bottas Closer to Mercedes Move Amid Williams Shake-Up
